data.description: Look no further than this beautiful 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home located in the Sierra Vista community of Clermont! This open and spacious layout is sure to catch your attention as soon as you walk through the front door. Off the foyer is the formal dining room currently used as a playroom that opens into the main livable space. With vaulted ceilings opening the rooms the spacious living room circles around into the kitchen and dinette. Granite countertops and sleek white cabinetry extend throughout the kitchen offering an abundance of counter space and storage. At the front of the house, you’ll find 2 guest bedrooms with a jack-n-jill bathroom in between and the additional guest bedroom and bathroom off the hallway. The primary bedroom tucked up at the back features a beautiful and spacious ensuite with a walk-in closet. Step outside to the fully screened back patio with your private pool enclosed with a child safety gate. Green space beyond that provides the perfect backyard and is fully fenced with vinyl fencing. Conveniently located in one of the best areas of Clermont, close to FL Turnpike, US50, US27, shops, restaurants, Lake-Sumter Community College, South Lake Hospital, Downtown Clermont, Orlando, Disney and the other parks, this house has it all. Schedule your private showing today!
